        "pythonCode": "import random\n\nenvironments = [\n    \"softly-lit outdoor garden surrounded by gentle natural foliage\",\n    \"cozy indoor kitchen with warm ambient lighting and wooden countertops\",\n    \"vibrant farmers market stall with colorful produce in the background\",\n    \"peaceful park bench under dappled oak tree sunlight\",\n    \"rustic countryside porch with flowering plants\",\n    \"modern cafe table near a sunny window\",\n    \"tropical beach setting with palm trees swaying gently\",\n    \"autumn forest clearing with golden leaves\",\n    \"spring meadow with wildflowers\",\n    \"urban rooftop garden at sunset\"\n]\n\nclothing = [\n    \"a blue and white striped shirt\",\n    \"a red plaid flannel shirt\",\n    \"a green hoodie with drawstrings\",\n    \"a yellow t-shirt with denim vest\",\n    \"a purple sweater\",\n    \"an orange polo shirt\",\n    \"a black and white baseball jersey\",\n    \"a brown cardigan\",\n    \"a teal windbreaker\",\n    \"a gray henley shirt\"\n]\n\nfood = [\n    \"a small chocolate chip cookie\",\n    \"a ripe banana slice\",\n    \"a tiny peanut butter sandwich\",\n    \"a fresh strawberry\",\n    \"a piece of mango\",\n    \"a mini donut\",\n    \"a small apple slice\",\n    \"a cookie with jam\",\n    \"a piece of watermelon\",\n    \"a tiny cupcake\"\n]\n\nselected_environment = random.choice(environments)\nselected_clothing = random.choice(clothing)\nselected_food = random.choice(food)\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"A cheerful young monkey wearing {selected_clothing} sits in {selected_environment}. The monkey holds {selected_food} and looks at it with wide, curious eyes. The monkey takes a bite and chews happily, eyes softening with contentment. After finishing, THE MONKEY'S FACE LIGHTS UP WITH A BIG, RADIANT SMILE and giggles joyfully - shoulders bouncing, eyes crinkling with pure delight. The monkey looks around playfully while smiling warmly, then settles into a gentle, satisfied smile with twinkling eyes.\n\nCRITICAL: The monkey must SMILE WIDELY and GIGGLE VISIBLY after eating. The smile and giggle are the emotional climax of the video.\n\nPhotorealistic, golden hour lighting, shallow depth of field, mid-chest framing. Facial expressions are the priority - especially the big smile and joyful giggle. Soft handheld camera motion. Natural, organic movements. Delicate ambient sounds with playful giggle.\"\"\"\n\nreturn {\"prompt\": prompt}"
      },
