      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "from datetime import datetime\nimport random\n\nVideo_Analysis = _input.first().json.content.parts[0].text\n\nnow = datetime.now()\ndate_str = now.strftime(\"%m/%d/%Y\")\ntime_str = now.strftime(\"%H:%M\")\n\n# Monkey/cute animal content hooks\nhook_phrases = [\n    \"POV: This monkey tried {food} and {reaction}\",\n    \"When {monkey_desc} tastes {food} for the first time {emotion}\",\n    \"This {monkey_desc} {action} and {consequence}\",\n    \"You won't believe how this monkey reacts to {food}\",\n    \"{monkey_desc} discovers {food} {reaction}\",\n    \"Watch this monkey's face when it tries {food} {emotion}\",\n    \"The moment {monkey_desc} realizes {discovery}\",\n    \"This little monkey {action} {consequence}\",\n    \"Nobody expected this monkey to {action}\",\n    \"{monkey_desc} eating {food} is {vibe}\"\n]\n\nmonkey_descriptions = [\n    \"adorable monkey\",\n    \"little monkey\",\n    \"curious monkey\",\n    \"happy monkey\",\n    \"cheerful monkey\",\n    \"sweet monkey\",\n    \"this precious monkey\",\n    \"baby monkey\",\n    \"silly monkey\",\n    \"playful monkey\"\n]\n\nfoods = [\n    \"fresh fruit\",\n    \"a juicy apple\",\n    \"sweet treats\",\n    \"snacks\",\n    \"delicious food\",\n    \"yummy treats\",\n    \"tasty snacks\",\n    \"something delicious\",\n    \"their favorite snack\",\n    \"a surprise treat\"\n]\n\nreactions = [\n    \"😍 the reaction is priceless\",\n    \"🐵 and the reaction melts hearts\",\n    \"the happiness is contagious\",\n    \"✨ pure joy happened\",\n    \"and it's the cutest thing ever\",\n    \"💚 instant happiness\",\n    \"you can see the joy\",\n    \"the smile says it all\",\n    \"🥰 wholesome overload\",\n    \"it's absolutely adorable\"\n]\n\nemotions = [\n    \"😊 and it's wholesome\",\n    \"🍎 pure happiness\",\n    \"and my heart melted\",\n    \"the cuteness is unreal\",\n    \"🐒 it's so precious\",\n    \"💕 most adorable thing\",\n    \"and I can't stop smiling\",\n    \"🌟 too cute to handle\",\n    \"instant serotonin boost\",\n    \"and it made my day\"\n]\n\nactions = [\n    \"tries new food\",\n    \"discovers treats\",\n    \"enjoys a snack\",\n    \"tastes something yummy\",\n    \"gets surprised by taste\",\n    \"reacts to food\",\n    \"enjoys their meal\",\n    \"has the best reaction\",\n    \"makes the cutest face\",\n    \"shows pure joy\"\n]\n\nconsequences = [\n    \"it's the cutest thing you'll see today\",\n    \"the reaction is priceless\",\n    \"you'll smile guaranteed\",\n    \"it's pure wholesomeness\",\n    \"your heart will melt\",\n    \"you'll want to watch on repeat\",\n    \"it's instant happiness\",\n    \"the joy is contagious\",\n    \"you can't help but smile\",\n    \"it's adorable overload\"\n]\n\ndiscoveries = [\n    \"food is amazing 🍎\",\n    \"treats are the best ✨\",\n    \"happiness tastes good 😋\",\n    \"snacks = pure joy 🐵\",\n    \"life is delicious 💚\",\n    \"this is the best day ever 🥰\",\n    \"food makes everything better\",\n    \"treats bring instant smiles 😊\",\n    \"yummy food = happy monkey 🌟\",\n    \"snack time is the best time\"\n]\n\nvibes = [\n    \"everything 🥰\",\n    \"pure wholesomeness 💚\",\n    \"the cutest content ✨\",\n    \"too adorable 🐵\",\n    \"instant serotonin 😊\",\n    \"heartwarming perfection 💕\",\n    \"absolutely precious 🌟\",\n    \"joy in its purest form\",\n    \"cuteness overload 😍\",\n    \"the best thing ever 🍎\"\n]\n\n# Generate title components\nmonkey_desc = random.choice(monkey_descriptions)\nfood = random.choice(foods)\nreaction = random.choice(reactions)\nemotion = random.choice(emotions)\naction = random.choice(actions)\nconsequence = random.choice(consequences)\ndiscovery = random.choice(discoveries)\nvibe = random.choice(vibes)\n\n# Create title\ntitle_template = random.choice(hook_phrases)\ntitle = title_template.format(\n    monkey_desc=monkey_desc,\n    food=food,\n    reaction=reaction,\n    emotion=emotion,\n    action=action,\n    consequence=consequence,\n    discovery=discovery,\n    vibe=vibe\n)\n\n# Ensure title is under 90 characters\nif len(title) > 90:\n    title = title[:87] + \"...\"\n\n# Build the prompt for AI node\nPrompt = f\"\"\"\nVideo Analysis Result:\n{Video_Analysis}\n\nBased on this cute monkey eating/reacting content, generate a structured JSON output for Google Sheets with the following fields:\n\n- \"Date\" (MM/DD/YYYY)\n- \"Time\" (HH:MM)\n- \"YouTubeTitle\" (catchy, emotional, cute, MUST be under 90 characters)\n- \"YouTubeTitle2\" (DIFFERENT catchy title, under 90 characters, use a different hook/angle than YouTubeTitle)\n- \"YouTubeDescription\" (engaging, wholesome, includes CTA like 'watch till the end' or 'tag someone who loves animals')\n- \"YouTubeDescription2\" (DIFFERENT description with different CTA and angle than YouTubeDescription)\n- \"TikTokDescription\" (short, punchy, instant cute factor)\n- \"FacebookReelDescription\" (attention-grabbing, shareable, feel-good vibes)\n- \"InstagramDescription\" (short, emoji-rich, engagement-focused)\n- \"AdditionalNotes\" (hashtags like #monkeylove #cuteanimals #animalreactions, trends, posting tips)\n\nCONTENT THEME: Cute monkey eating food, adorable reactions, wholesome animal content, happiness, joy, heartwarming moments\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n1. Both \"YouTubeTitle\" and \"YouTubeTitle2\" MUST NOT exceed 90 characters.\n2. YouTubeTitle and YouTubeTitle2 MUST be COMPLETELY DIFFERENT - use different psychological hooks (surprise vs cuteness vs joy vs relatability).\n3. YouTubeDescription and YouTubeDescription2 MUST be COMPLETELY DIFFERENT - vary the CTAs and emotional angles.\n4. All content must match the cute/wholesome/animal content theme.\n5. Use warm, joyful, uplifting language that makes people smile.\n6. Focus on feelings: happiness, cuteness, joy, wholesome vibes, heartwarming, adorable.\n7. The \"Date\" and \"Time\" should be accurate based on the current date and time provided below:\n   - CurrentDate: {date_str}\n   - CurrentTime: {time_str}\n8. The output MUST be valid JSON, properly escaped.\n\nTITLE STYLE EXAMPLES (use these psychological angles):\n- Reaction: \"This monkey's reaction to food is TOO cute 🐵\"\n- POV: \"POV: You just made a monkey's day with snacks 🍎\"\n- Surprise: \"Watch what happens when this monkey tries treats 😍\"\n- Relatable: \"Me when someone brings snacks to the function 🐒\"\n- Wholesome: \"Pure joy on this little monkey's face 💚\"\n\nDESCRIPTION STYLE EXAMPLES:\n- Wholesome: \"The way this little monkey enjoys every bite is pure happiness 🥰 Sometimes the simplest things bring the biggest smiles. Who else loves watching animals enjoying their food? Drop a 💚 below!\"\n- Engaging: \"That REACTION though! 😍 You can see the exact moment the monkey realizes how good it tastes. Have you ever seen something this wholesome? Watch till the end for the best part!\"\n- Relatable: \"Honestly same energy when I try something delicious 🐵✨ This monkey is living its best life and I'm here for it. Tag someone who reacts like this to good food 🍎\"\n\nExample structure:\n{{\n  \"Date\": \"{date_str}\",\n  \"Time\": \"{time_str}\",\n  \"YouTubeTitle\": \"{title}\",\n  \"YouTubeTitle2\": \"...\",\n  \"YouTubeDescription\": \"...\",\n  \"YouTubeDescription2\": \"...\",\n  \"TikTokDescription\": \"...\",\n  \"FacebookReelDescription\": \"...\",\n  \"InstagramDescription\": \"...\",\n  \"AdditionalNotes\": \"...\"\n}}\n\nCRITICAL: \n- YouTubeTitle and YouTubeTitle2 must use DIFFERENT psychological angles (cute vs funny vs heartwarming vs relatable).\n- YouTubeDescription and YouTubeDescription2 must tell DIFFERENT emotional stories.\n- DO NOT repeat the same content.\n- Focus on creating instant positive emotions and shareability.\n- Make viewers feel joy and want to share with friends.\n- Emphasize the REACTION and EMOTIONS of the monkey based on the video analysis.\n\n- Generate engaging, high-CTR titles and descriptions that create warmth, joy, and instant smiles.\n- DO NOT COPY THE TITLES OF THE EXAMPLES PROVIDED TO YOU! CREATE ORIGINAL TITLES BASED ON THE VIDEO ANALYSIS!\n- Pay attention to the monkey's actual reaction in the video (surprise, happiness, wide eyes, laughter, etc.) and reflect that in titles/descriptions.\n\"\"\"\n\nreturn {\n    \"chatInput\": Prompt\n}"
      },
